descriptionNullable: This dataset captures the purchase behavior of customers during the Diwali season across different states and zones of India. It contains details such as the customer's name, gender, age group, marital status, state of residence, occupational sector, product category, number of orders, and purchase amount. The information provided offers insights into the demographic and economic aspects of the buying patterns during one of India's most significant festivals.
title: Diwali Sales Dataset (India)
subtitle: Diwali Purchase Patterns in India
description: This dataset captures the purchase behavior of customers during the Diwali season across different states and zones of India. It contains details such as the customer's name, gender, age group, marital status, state of residence, occupational sector, product category, number of orders, and purchase amount. The information provided offers insights into the demographic and economic aspects of the buying patterns during one of India's most significant festivals.
